          "Given a supported connected cooling appliance reports no temperature-controlled zones, when the dashboard is displayed, then no zone temperature value is shown for that appliance.",
          "Given a temperature-controlled zone is reported but its latest available temperature value is unavailable, when the dashboard is displayed, then the zone remains represented and the temperature field shows a defined unavailable-temperature fallback instead of an incorrect numeric value."
        ],
